{
  "stem": "25423.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Until-- I was hiding in the apartment for a few days, but my suggestion is-- this, needless to say, is a central event of my experiences under the Germans which, in a way, has dictated a variety of things at a later date.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I have written a book, [NON-ENGLISH], which was published in Eretz, Israel, or Palestine, in 1947 or '46 by [NON-ENGLISH], describing in great detail this particular incident.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I also have written an article, which was published in the Ukraine in [NON-ENGLISH] Academy of Science.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then, recently, I published a book, published in the United States by Fithian Press, and I described this particular instance in great detail.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Therefore, there is probably no need to dwell on it more.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I was hiding while these people were running around loose in the streets catching Jews.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And once this subsided-- I don't look particularly Jewish-- why, one day I decided, after two or three days, that's enough.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So, I washed up, put on a suit, and went out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's the end of it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, she wasn't aware of that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a lengthy process because, you see, my mother knew that my father went to [NON-ENGLISH] to the Metropolitan.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He offered him shelter, and there was-- a rumor circulated that he was hidden by the Metropolitan, which I knew was not true because I've seen him shot.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I didn't go out of my way to tell it to my mother.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The next day after this incident, two SS men came.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They had a list, and asked for my father.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So, my mother said he was taken away.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So, they beat her up and left.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
